   Some additional books 
       
   Colin Ware, Information Visualization, 2 nd  Edition:
  Perception for Design, Morgan Kaufmann, 2004. 
       
   Martin  Helander , Ed., Handbook
  of Human-Computer Interaction, North-Holland, 1986. 
       
   Martin  Helander , Thomas  Landauer , and Prasad  Prabhu ,
  eds., Handbook of Human-Computer Interaction, 2 nd  Edition,
  North-Holland, 1997. 
       
   Herbert Simon, The Sciences of the Artificial, The MIT
  Press, (any edition is okay), 1969 (1 st  edition), 1981 (2 nd 
  edition), 1996 (3 rd  edition). 
       
   Stuart Card, Jock  Mackinlay , Ben
   Shneiderman , Eds., Readings in Information Visualization:
  Using Vision to Think, Morgan Kaufmann, 1999. 
       
   Benjamin   Bederson    �  and  Ben  Shneiderman , Eds., The Craft of Information
  Visualization: Readings
  and Reflections, Morgan Kaufmann, 2003. 
       
   Robert  Klanten , Nicolas  Bourquin ,  Thibaud   Tissot , Sven  Ehmann , Data Flow:
   Visualising  Information in Graphic Design,
  Gestalten, 2008. 
       
   Jim Foley, John T.  Stasko , John
  B.  Domingue , and Marc H. Brown, Software
  Visualization, The MIT Press, 1998. 
       
   And all the books by Edward  Tufte 
  see website listed above. 
   
   
       
   
    
         
   
   
       
   
   
       
   
    
         
   
   
       
   
   
       
   
    
         
   
   
       
   
   
       
   
        

     

     

 

